        "caption": "List of pulsation and chemical properties for high-velocity RR~Lyrae candidates found in our analysis. The first column lists our adopted object ID. Columns 2 and 3 provide the star's pulsation period $P$ and amplitude of the total light changes based on the CSS photometry. In the last two columns, we list the assumed RR~Lyrae sub-class and metallicity derived using the $\\Delta$S method. Similarly to Table~\\ref{tab:HV-RR} we marked variables with uncertain classification with an asterisk.",
