        "caption": "Table of unbound RR Lyrae candidates with $P_{\\rm unb} > 0.5$ and their astrometric and photometric properties from \\gaia~catalog. The first column represents our object ID with an asterisk marking variables uncertain classification as RR~Lyrae stars. Columns 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6 lists \\gaia~EDR3 ID, equatorial and Galactic coordinates. The proper motions in right ascension and declination, together with their errors, are listed in columns 7, 8, 9, and 10. Columns 11 and 12 contain parallax and its uncertainty. The last three columns (13, 14 and 15) represent re-normalized unit weight error (RUWE) and \\gaia~photometry in $G$-band and color $G_{\\rm BP} - G_{\\rm RP}$.",
